"  >Alumni</a></span></div><ul><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="alumni/overview/" title="European Graduate School - Alumni Overview"  >Overview</a></li><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="alumni/alumni-association/" title="European Graduate School - Alumni Association"  >Alumni Association</a></li><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="alumni/alumni-directory/" title="European Graduate School - Alumni Directory"  >Alumni Directory</a></li><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="alumni/alumni-news/" title="European Graduate School - Alumni News"  >Alumni News</a></li><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="alumni/event-calendar/" title="Alumni and academic calendar of European Graduate School EGS, Media and Communication studies program, featuring dates, events, and deadlines"  >Event Calendar</a></li><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="alumni/request-transcripts/" title="European Graduate School - Request Transcripts"  >Request Transcripts</a></li><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="alumni/giving-to-egs/" title="European Graduate School - Giving to EGS"  >Giving to EGS</a></li></ul></li><li class="menuparent"><div class="headline"><span class="headline_link"><a href="faculty/faculty-overview/" title="Faculty"  >Faculty</a></span></div><ul><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="faculty/faculty-overview/" title="European Graduate School - Faculty Overview"  >Faculty Overview</a></li><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="faculty/faculty-news/" title="European Graduate School - Faculty News"  >Faculty News</a></li><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="faculty/event-calendar/" title="Faculty and academic calendar of European Graduate School EGS, Media and Communication studies program, featuring dates, events, and deadlines"  >Event Calendar</a></li><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="faculty/video-lectures/egs-video-lectures-2012/" title="Video Lectures"  >Video Lectures</a></li><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="faculty/jobs-and-positions/" title="European Graduate School - Jobs and Positions"  >Jobs and Positions</a></li></ul></li><li class="menuparent"><div class="headline"><span class="headline_link"><a href="media/publications/" title="Media"  >Media</a></span></div><ul><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="media/publications/" title="European Graduate School - EGS Publications"  >EGS Publications</a></li><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="media/egs-on-facebook/" title="EGS on Facebook"  >EGS on Facebook</a></li><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="media/egs-on-youtube/" title="EGS on YouTube"  >EGS on YouTube</a></li><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="media/egs-on-google/" title="EGS on Google+"  >EGS on Google+</a></li><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="media/egs-on-flickr/" title="European Graduate School - EGS on Flickr"  >EGS on Flickr</a></li><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="media/egs-on-twitter/" title="EGS on Twitter"  >EGS on Twitter</a></li><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="media/conferences-festivals/" title="European Graduate School - Conferences &amp; Festivals"  >Conferences & Festivals</a></li><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="library/" title="European Graduate School - Library / Encyclopedia"  >Library / Encyclopedia</a></li><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="media/research-database/" title="European Graduate School - Research Database"  >Research Database</a></li></ul></li><li class="menuparent"><div class="headline"><span class="headline_link"><a href="resources/a-z-index/" title="Resources"  >Resources</a></span></div><ul><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="resources/news/" title="European Graduate School - News"  >News</a></li><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="resources/event-calendar/" title="Academic calendar of European Graduate School EGS, Media and Communication studies program, featuring dates, events, and deadlines"  >Event Calendar</a></li><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="resources/information-technology/" title="European Graduate School - Information Technology"  >Information Technology</a></li><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="resources/health-services/" title="European Graduate School - Health Services"  >Health Services</a></li><li>&raquo;&nbsp;<a href="resources/a-z-index/" title="European Graduate School - A-Z Index"  >A-Z Index</a></li