				<div id="content-area">

					<p>The School of Journalism and Communication offers undergraduate programs including the Bachelor of Journalism and Bachelor of Arts in Communication Studies. In addition, we offer graduate programs including the Master of Journalism, Master of Arts in Communication, and PhD in Communication.</p>
						
